reviewText: movie was pretty cool if you're a biker you'll dig it unless you're into harleys but for the money its an excellent buy im happy with it of course the most extreme i get is standing up and doing wheelies these guys are a little nuts on the bikes
I loved it... lots of stupid idiots busting their buns for my entertainment..... don't let your kids watch it unless you want them to try being stupid on their motorcycles.
